(9, 'pt-br', 'Campus Santo Antônio', '<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><div style=\"text-align:center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;\"><div style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"http://192.168.2.175/assets/files/slide csa (2) (1).jpg\"></div><br></span></div><div style=\"text-align:center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;\"><br></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font face=\"Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;\">O Campus Santo Antônio, onde está instalada a Reitoria, é a mais antiga edificação da UFSJ, fazendo parte do conjunto arquitetônico tombado na cidade histórica de São João del-Rei.</span><br></font></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Arial\"><br></font></span></div></div><div><span class=\"text-title\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-897b2e41-7fff-fd0c-ab4b-275c3a49e3ea\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\">O primeiro prédio desta edificação foi o Pavilhão Sul, inaugurado em 1917, pelos religiosos franciscanos que ali fundaram, em 1909, o Ginásio Santo Antônio, tradicional colégio que formou gerações de estudantes até 1972. Com o fim do educandário, no “Santo Antônio” funcionou até 1987 a Fundação Municipal de São João del-Rei,&nbsp; instituição universitária que deu origem à UFSJ.</font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\"><br></font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\">Ao longo do tempo, reformas e instalações foram realizadas para condicionar o espaço físico ao funcionamento de uma universidade pública. Entre as construções, destacam-se a Biblioteca, que abriga um moderno anfiteatro e os novos prédios dos Departamentos de Engenharia Mecânica e de Engenharia Elétrica.</font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\"><br></font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\">Neste campus, além da Reitoria, estão instaladas as Pró-Reitorias de Administração (Proad) , de Ensino de Graduação (Proen), de Planejamento (Pplan), de Assuntos Estudantis (Proae), além da de Gestão e Desenvolvimento de Pessoas (Progp). Os cursos de Engenharia Elétrica, Engenharia Mecânica, Engenharia de Produção e Matemática funcionam neste campus.</font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\">&nbsp;</font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\">Endereço do Campus Santo Antônio</font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\">Praça Frei Orlando, 170 – Centro – São João del-Rei</font></span></div><div><br></div></span></span></div>', 3),
(10, 'en-us', 'Santo Antonio Campus', '<div><div style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"http://192.168.2.175/assets/files/slide csa (2) (1).jpg\"></div><br></div><div><div><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-908fef9d-7fff-e73a-45f0-c365304f5032\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\">The Santo Antônio <i>Campus</i>, where the Rectory is located, is the oldest UFSJ building, and is part of the listed architectural complex at the historical city of São joão del-Rei.&nbsp;</font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\"><br></font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\">The first building of this property was the South Pavilion, erected in 1917 by&nbsp; the religious Franciscan who founded, in 1909, the Santo Antônio Gymnasium, a traditional high school that educated generations of students until 1972.&nbsp; Later, this school stopped functioning. With the end of this school, the university institution called Municipal Foundation of São João del-Rei, operated in the “Santo Antônio” building until 1987, later on giving rise to UFSJ.</font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\"><br></font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\">Over time, renewals and installations were carried out to condition the physical space for the functioning of a public university. Among the constructions, the library, which houses a modern amphitheater, and the new buildings of the Departments of Mechanical and Electrical Engineering Department stand out.&nbsp;</font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\"><br></font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\">At this campus, besides the Rectory, are installed the Dean’s Offices for Administration (Proad), for Undergraduate Education (Proen), for Planning (Pplan), for Student Affairs (Proae), in addition to the Office of People Management and Development (Progp). The undergraduate courses of Electrical Engineering, Mechanical Engineering, Production Engineering, and Mathematics are present at this campus.&nbsp;</font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font face=\"Arial\">&nbsp;</font></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\">&nbsp;Santo Antônio <i>Campus </i>Address:</font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\">Praça Frei Orlando, 170 – Centro – São João del-Rei</font></span></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><br></span></div></span></div><div><br></div></div>', 3),
