(73, 'pt-br', 'Campus Dom Bosco', '<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><div style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"http://192.168.2.175/assets/files/slide cdb (1) (1).jpg\"></div><br></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b><br></b></div><div><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-c06b0484-7fff-66b0-46a7-915ff462e927\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\">Situado no Bairro das Fábricas, o Campus Dom Bosco teve seu início em 1940, com a fundação do Colégio São João, dirigido pelos religiosos salesianos que se instalaram na cidade. Posteriormente, em 1987, o Campus foi adquirido pelo Ministério da Educação.</font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\"><br></font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\">A partir de então, várias adaptações foram realizadas no prédio principal e outros prédios foram construídos para atender as necessidades institucionais. Entre elas, destacam-se a Biblioteca, dotada de anfiteatro e sala climatizada para guarda de obras raras, e os prédios dos Departamentos de Ciências Naturais (Dcnat), de Medicina (Demed) e de Biossistemas (Depeb).</font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\"><br></font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font face=\"Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\">Neste <i>Campus</i>, está instalada a Pró-Reitoria de Pesquisa e Pós-Graduação (Prope), bem como os cursos de graduação em Letras, Psico</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12pt;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\">logia, Física, Química, Filosofia, Pedagogia, História, Ciências Biológicas, Medicina e Biotecnologia.</span></font></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\">&nbsp;</font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12pt;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\">Endereço do <i>Campus </i>Dom Bosco</font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\">Praça Dom Helvécio, 74 – Bairro Fábricas – São João del-Rei</font></span></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><br></span></div></span></div>', 19),
(74, 'en-us', 'Dom Bosco Campus', '<div><div style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"http://192.168.2.175/assets/files/slide cdb (1) (1).jpg\"></div><br></div><br><div><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-9be1a2a9-7fff-4814-51e4-19fc64e59d3f\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\">Located in the Fábricas neighborhood, the Dom Bosco <i>Campus </i>had its beginnings in 1940, with the foundation of Colégio São João, run by the Salesian religious who settled in the city. Later, in 1987, the <i>Campus </i>was acquired by the Education Ministry.&nbsp;</font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\"><br></font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font face=\"Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\">Since then, several adaptations have been made to the main building, and also other buildings were constructed to meet the institutional needs. Among them are the library, which houses an amphitheater and a climatized room to keep rare works safe, and the buildings of the Departments of Natural Sciences (Dcnat), Medicine (Demed), and Biosystems (Depeb)</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12pt;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\">.</span></font></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12pt;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\"><br></font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\">At this campus, it is installed the Office of Research and Graduate Studies (Prope), as well as the undergraduate courses in Modern Languages (Portuguese and English), Psychology, Chemistry, Philosophy, Pedagogy, History, Biological Sciences, Medicine, and Biotechnology.</font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font face=\"Arial\">&nbsp;</font></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\">Dom Bosco <i>Campus </i>Address:</font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\">Praça Dom Helvécio, 74 – Bairro Fábricas – São João del-Rei</font></span></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><br></span></div></span></div>', 19),
