(78, 'en-us', 'Rector&#39;s Office', '<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-3e7e6445-7fff-13b6-b9e5-559e8e622fb9\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\">The Rectory is the general administrative body that coordinates, executes, and supervises all the university activities, accomplishing and enforcing the regulations and deliberations of the Higher Councils. The Rector and the Vice-Rector, holders of the Rector’s office, are elected by the university community, and the Rector is appointed by the President of the Federative Republic of Brazil, according to the legislation in effect.</span></div><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><br>\r\n<b><br></b><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>Current Administration&nbsp; 2020-2024</b></div></span><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><div style=\"text-align:center;\"><div style=\"text-align:center;\"><b><img src=\"http://192.168.2.175/assets/files/ufsj-marcelo (1).jpg\"></b></div></div></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 10pt;=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" 700;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><b>Professor Marcelo Pereira de Andrade</b></span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.3333px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><b>Rector</b></span></font></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" 700;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><b>Appointment: 9/5/2020</b></span></