(97, 'pt-br', 'RESTAURANTES UNIVERSITÁRIOS', '<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-38130fc6-7fff-ebdd-cf5b-43ebdb8ec24a\"><div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><font face=\"Arial\">Os restaurantes universitários fazem parte das ações de assistência estudantil do Programa Nacional de Assistência Estudantil (PNAES) e são previstos pelo Decreto nª 7.234, de 19 de julho de 2010. Tal ação visa garantir a produção e o fornecimento de refeições para a comunidade universitária, sobretudo os discentes, visando favorecer as condições adequadas para integração e desenvolvimento nos diferentes segmentos da vida universitária.</font></span></div><font face=\"Arial\"><font color=\"#000000\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br></span></div></font><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-size: 12pt;\">Na UFSJ, contamos com seis (6) restaurantes universitários, sendo que destes, três estão localizados nos campi localizados na cidade de São João del-Rei (Restaurante do Campus Dom Bosco, Restaurante do Campus Tancredo Neves e Restaurante do Campus Santo Antônio) e três nos campi localizados em outras cidades (Restaurante do Campus Alto Paraopeba, em Ouro Branco; Restaurante do Campus Centro-Oeste Dona Lindu, em Divinópolis; e Restaurante do Campus Sete Lagoas, em Sete Lagoas).&nbsp;</span></div></span><font color=\"#000000\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br></span></div></font><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-size: 12pt;\">Nesses restaurantes, a UFSJ oferece almoço e jantar, para alunos regularmente matriculados em cursos de graduação presencial e o valor de cada refeição é de R$2,75 .</span></div></span></font></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><br><br></span></div></span>', 25),
(98, 'en-us', 'UNIVERSITY RESTAURANTS', '<div><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-ee314716-7fff-7404-fc77-4b5fdf7710e8\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><font face=\"Arial\">The university restaurants are part of the student assistance actions of the National Student Assistance Program (PNAES), and are supported by Decree No. 7.234, dated from July 19th, 2013. This action aims to ensure the production and supply of meals for the university community, especially students, in order to favour the appropriate conditions for the integration and development in different segments of university life.</font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><font face=\"Arial\"><br></font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><font face=\"Arial\">At UFSJ, we have six (6) university restaurants, three of which are located on the campuses in São João del-Rei (Dom Bosco Campus Restaurant, Tancredo Neves Campus Restaurant. and Santo Antônio Campus Restaurant), and three located on campuses in other cities (Alto Paraopeba Campus Restaurant, in Ouro Branco City; Dona Lindu Midwest Campus Restaurant, in Divinópolis City; and Sete Lagoas Campus Restaurant, in Sete Lagoas City).</font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><font face=\"Arial\">At these restaurants, UFSJ offers lunch and dinner for students regularly enrolled in undergraduate courses, and the value of each meal is 2,75 reals.</font></span></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><br></span></div></span></div>', 25),
