=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><font face=\"Arial\">Brasília: 910 Km,&nbsp;about&nbsp;10 hours.</font></span></div><div><div><span><span style=\"\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Arial\"><div style=\"\"><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\"><div style=\"\"><div style=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"></span></div></div></div></span></div></font></span></span></div></div>', 27),
