(121, 'pt-br', 'Fortim dos Emboabas (Centro de Referência de Cultura Max Justo Guedes)', '<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a0f9c0ff-7fff-3bfb-ab5e-a7f18501a886\"><div><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><div style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"http://192.168.2.175/assets/files/fortim2.png\"></div><div style=\"text-align:center;\"><br></div><br></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\">O casarão, um dos mais antigos da cidade, foi recebido pela Universidade Federal de São João Del-Rei, por doação, em 2009, sendo tombado na instância municipal e federal, dado o seu inestimável valor histórico. Sua localização já antecipa seu inquestionável valor, visto que no bairro Alto das Mercês, há uma grande quantidade de vestígios e marcas históricas. Um exemplo seriam as betas, túneis cavados por garimpeiros do século 18. Segundo a tradição oral, o espaço físico do Centro serviu de forte a portugueses e brasileiros do norte, que nela se entrincheiravam contra o ataque dos paulistas durante a Guerra dos Emboabas, ocorrida entre 1707 e 1709. Seu nome se deve ao fato de ter sido propriedade do Almirante Max Justo Guedes.</font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\"><br></font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\">O Fortim é sede do Projeto de Extensão \"Centro de Referência de Cultura Popular Max Justo Guedes\" do qual fazem parte o Museu do Barro e o Museu de Vivências. A&nbsp; professora Glória Maria (DFIME), coordenadora&nbsp; do&nbsp; projeto,&nbsp; destaca&nbsp; a&nbsp; importância&nbsp; do Fortim &nbsp; para a comunidade do Alto das Mercês, dado que, a implantação de um centro de cultura popular da universidade&nbsp; no&nbsp; bairro,&nbsp; avulta a&nbsp; importância&nbsp; da&nbsp; cultura de matriz africana para a constituição da identidade da cidade.</font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\"><br></font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\">A &nbsp; professora&nbsp; Zandra Coelho de &nbsp; Miranda (DAUAP), acrescenta ainda que o Centro possui importância estratégica para a preservação do patrimônio imaterial de São João del-Rei e região. Segundo ela, essa história, contada por este conjunto de artefatos, está registrada em documentos com pouquíssimas palavras, o que abre espaço de produção de&nbsp; conhecimento&nbsp; a&nbsp; partir destes sobreviventes.&nbsp; Em outros termos, há um campo de estudos riquíssimo, ainda pouco explorado.</font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font face=\"Arial\"><br></font></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\">Centro de Referência de Cultura Max Justo Guedes (Fortim dos Emboabas), localizado na Rua Altamiro Flor, 0, Alto das Mercês, São João Del-Rei.</font></span></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><br></span></div></span>', 31),
(122, 'en-us', 'Max Justo Guedes Culture Reference Centre (also known as Fortim dos Emboabas)', '<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-44a24486-7fff-9cb5-4940-c912ba49ef8c\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12pt;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><div style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"http://192.168.2.175/assets/files/fortim2.png\"></div><div style=\"text-align:center;\"><br></div><br></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12pt;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\">The building, one of oldest in the city, was earned by the Federal University of São João del-Rei through donation in 2009,&nbsp; and was listed in the municipal and federal level, considering its priceless historical value. Its localization already anticipates its unquestionable value, considering that in the neighbourhood of Alto das Mercês there are a lot of traces and historical marks. An example would be the “betas”, which are tunnels dug by gold prospectors&nbsp; during the 18th century. </font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12pt;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\"><br></font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font face=\"Arial\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12pt;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\">According to the oral tradition, the physical space of the centre served as a fort for the Portuguese and Brazilians from the north, entrenched there against the attacks of Paulistas (people from the state of São Paulo) during the War of the Emboabas, occurred between 1707 and 1709. Its name is due to the fact that it was owned by Admiral Max Justo Guedes.</span><br></font></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12pt;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\"><br></font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\">The “Fortim” is the headquarters of the extension project called “Max Justo Guedes&nbsp; Popular Culture Reference Centre”, which includes the Clay Museum and the Experience Museum. Professor Glória Maria (DFIME), coordinator of the project, highlights the importance of the Fortim for the community of Alto das Mercês, considering that the implementation of a centre of popular culture of the university in the neighbourhood reinforces the importance of the culture of African origin for the constitution of the city’s identity.</font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\"><br></font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font face=\"Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\">Professor Zandra Coelho de Miranda (DAUAP) also adds that the Centre has strategic importance for the preservation of the intangible heritage of São João del-Rei and region. According to her, this history, told by this set of artefacts, is registered in documents with very few words, which opens space to the production of knowledge from these survivors. In </span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" 700;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\">Max Justo Guedes Culture Reference Centre</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"> (also known as Fortim dos Emboabas), located at Rua Altamiro Flor, 0, Alto das Mercês, São João Del-Rei.</span></font></div><div><br></div></span>', 31),
