(185, 'pt-br', 'Engenharia Agronômica', '<div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\ncolor:rgb(34,34,34);font-size:12,0000pt;\">Titulação: Bacharel em Engenharia Agronômica</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\ncolor:rgb(34,34,34);font-size:12,0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\ncolor:rgb(34,34,34);font-size:12,0000pt;\">Número de vagas: 80 vagas por ano, sendo 40 vagas por semestre</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\ncolor:rgb(34,34,34);font-size:12,0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\ncolor:rgb(34,34,34);font-size:12,0000pt;\">Carga horária total: 3.782,5 horas</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\ncolor:rgb(34,34,34);font-size:12,0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\ncolor:rgb(34,34,34);font-size:12,0000pt;\">Prazos de Integralização: Padrão: 5 anos; Máximo: 7,5 anos e&nbsp; Mínimo: 5</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\ncolor:rgb(34,34,34);font-size:12,0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\ncolor:rgb(34,34,34);font-size:12,0000pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\ncolor:rgb(34,34,34);font-size:12,0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\ncolor:rgb(34,34,34);font-size:12,0000pt;\">O Campus Sete Lagoas (CSL) está localizado na Mesorregião Metropolitana de Belo Horizonte e Microrregião de Sete Lagoas. Sua área de influência, com mais de 500.000 habitantes.&nbsp; A inserção do CSL/UFSJ no contexto regional é estratégica, prevendo atuação nas diferentes áreas das Ciências Agrárias, com base em uma formação teórica e prática, aliada à pesquisa científica, extensão e cooperações com outras instituições de ensino e pesquisa.</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\ncolor:rgb(34,34,34);font-size:12,0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\ncolor:rgb(34,34,34);font-size:12,0000pt;\"><br></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\ncolor:rgb(34,34,34);font-size:12,0000pt;\">A localização geográfica do CSL, próxima à Embrapa Milho e Sorgo (CNPMS/EMBRAPA) e à EPAMIG Centro Oeste, facilita as parcerias interinstitucionais, inclusive quanto à integração dos estudantes da UFSJ em projetos de iniciação científica e estágios. Destaca-se também a forte cooperação existente entre a Prefeitura Municipal de Sete Lagoas e a UFSJ, com estágios em diversos setores do município.</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\ncolor:rgb(34,34,34);font-size:12,0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\ncolor:rgb(34,34,34);font-size:12,0000pt;\"><br></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\ncolor:rgb(34,34,34);font-size:12,0000pt;\">Atividades da graduação são também desenvolvidas em integração com o Programa de Pós-Graduação em Ciências Agrárias da UFSJ (PPGCA). Neste programa, ressalta-se a parceria entre as instituições UFSJ, EMBRAPA e EPAMIG.</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\ncolor:rgb(34,34,34);font-size:12,0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></div></div>', 47),
(186, 'en-us', 'Agronomic Engineering', '<div><div><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;\r\nfont-size:12,0000pt;\">Course: Agronomic Engineering</span></div><div><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;\r\nfont-size:12,0000pt;\">Title: Bachelor’s Degree in Agronomic Engineering</span></div><div><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;\r\nfont-size:12,0000pt;\">Number of seats: 80 per year, or 40 per semester </span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;\r\nfont-size:12,0000pt;\">&nbsp;= </span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;\r\nfont-size:12,0000pt;\">Total workload: 3,782.5 hours</span></div><div><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;\r\nfont-size:12,0000pt;\">Deadline for completion: Standard: 5 years; Maximum: 7.5 years; Minimum: 5 years </span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;\r\nfont-size:12,0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></div><div><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;\r\nfont-size:12,0000pt;\"><br></span></div><div><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;\r\nfont-size:12,0000pt;\"><br></span></div><div><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;\r\nfont-size:12,0000pt;\">Campus Sete Lagoas (CSL) is located in the Metropolitan Mesoregion of Belo Horizonte and the Microregion of Sete Lagoas. It has an area of influence with more than 500,000 habitants. The insertion of CSL/UFSJ in the regional context is strategic, providing for action in the different areas of Agricultural Sciences, based on the theoretical and practical training, combined with scientific research, extension and cooperation with other teaching and research institutions. </span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;\r\nfont-size:12,0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></div><div><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;\r\nfont-size:12,0000pt;\"><br></span></div><div><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;\r\nfont-size:12,0000pt;\">The geographical location of CSL &nbsp;close to Embrapa Corn and Sorghum (CNPMS/EMBRAPA) and EPAMIG Centro Oeste facilitates inter-institutional partnerships, including the integration of UFSJ students in scientific initiation projects and internships. Also noteworthy is the strong cooperation between the municipality of Sete Lagoas and UFSJ, with internships in various sectors of the municipality. </span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;\r\nfont-size:12,0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></div><div><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;\r\nfont-size:12,0000pt;\"><br></span></div><div><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;\r\nfont-size:12,0000pt;\">Undergraduate activities are also developed in integration with the graduate program in agricultural sciences at UFSJ (PPGCA). In this program, the partnership between UFSJ, EMBRAPA and EPAMIG stands out.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;\r\nfont-size:12,0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></div></div>', 47),
